      <title>即将到来的遗产继承浪潮、数据成本、欧盟的竞争权衡 | 华尔街周刊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/coming-wave-of-inheritance-cost-of-data-eu-s-competition-tradeoff-wall-street-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本期《华尔街周刊》中，我们将关注 105 万亿美元的遗产继承潮，这波浪潮可能会集中体现财富动态、美国统计数据的侵蚀以及欧盟在监管竞争和促进创新之间的平衡。我们还将与 Centerview Partners 高级顾问 Richard Haass 一起探讨公民教育的现状。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-20/coming-wave-of-inheritance-cost-of-data-eu-s-competition-tradeoff-wall-street-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 23:28:35 GMT</pubDate>
